Detailed Description

This Structure is used for storing results of TESOC test. These parameters are used as place holder for storing result.

Field Documentation

uint32_t tesocAdvanceResult::abortFlag

Flag for detecting TESOC test Abort

uint32_t tesocAdvanceResult::domainLabel

Domain label for running TESOC test on. Refer enum #tesocDomainLabel_t for details

uint32_t tesocAdvanceResult::errorLog[TESOC_DIAG_LOG_CYCLES][TESOC_DIAG_LOG_DATA_SIZE]

On test failure TESOC dumps TESOC_DIAG_LOG_CYCLES cycles of data. Each cycle of data is of size TESOC_DIAG_LOG_DATA_SIZE.

int32_t tesocAdvanceResult::failedSliceNumber

Slice number of failed slice after TESOC execution, value of (-1) if none failed

uint32_t tesocAdvanceResult::sliceResult[TESOC_NUM_SLICE_BLOCKS]

Result of slices configured for TESOC test

uint32_t tesocAdvanceResult::sliceStatus[TESOC_NUM_SLICE_BLOCKS]

Status of slices configured for TESOC test
